                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-19-off99 t18170917-19-cd100"></join> (no person being therein), with intent to steal, and stealing therein, one table-cloth, value 4d.; one handkerchief, value 6d.; one pair of breeches, value 5s.; one coat, value 6s.; one gown, value 2s., and five caps, value 5s.
            </rs>, his property.</p>
